@NODE AM-4 "History of the program"
1.0 (6.7.93) first release.

1.1 (9.7.93) and the next follows.
 - bug fixed: memory loss if no NAME/M argument was given.
 - code optimized.
 - the listed sizes of "#?.guide" files were false.

1.2 (28.7.93)
 - writing full names only by assigns and "" (current directory)
   now (icon.library's PutDiskObject() don't handle both).
 - added new arguments: ALL and QUIET.
 - extended error mesages.
@ENDNODE
